Hi,<br />
This should be possible if you set the chart attribute &quot;SelectedBrush&quot; to &quot;Transparent&quot;.<br />
<pre><code>&lt;chart:ClusteredColumnChart  
        ChartTitle=&quot;Column Chart&quot;
        ChartSubTitle=&quot;Chart with fixed width and height&quot; 
        ...
        SelectedBrush=&quot;Transparent&quot; &gt;
        &lt;chart:ClusteredColumnChart.Series&gt;
            ...
        &lt;/chart:ClusteredColumnChart.Series&gt;
    &lt;/chart:ClusteredColumnChart&gt;
</code></pre>

Cheers,<br />
Torsten<br />
